Get Repo
--------

    mkdir ~/bin
    export PATH=~/bin:$PATH
    curl https://dl-ssl.google.com/dl/googlesource/git-repo/repo > ~/bin/repo
    chmod a+x ~/bin/repo

Syncing the XY Source
---------------------------------------

    mkdir ~/aosp
    cd ~/aosp
    repo init -u https://github.com/s2heros/android -b patch-1

    repo sync -j 4 | 8 | 16 | 24 | 32
